awscc_appstream_image_builder (Data Source)

Data Source schema for AWS::AppStream::ImageBuilder

Read-Only

  • domain_join_info (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
  • enable_default_internet_access (Boolean)

  • image_arn (String)
  • image_name (String)
  • instance_type (String)
  • name (String)
  • streaming_url (String)
  • tags (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)
  • vpc_config (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
